{"tid":1500680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民對抗CCMTR，集氣Post","createTime":"2019-08-24T05:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:46:19.000Z","uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebfe8e8a5e8677f0f90cad38fd29fbf7e21c3ee","tid":1500680,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:59:15.000Z","msg":"人民日報一出post，HKCCMTR就立即跪低。人神共憤，作為一間大型公共運輸系統。不合理地話停就停，話關閘就關閘。<br />\n<br />\n作為蟻民嘅我地係咪就咁就算？希望大家可以多d討論下點樣可以對抗下CCMTR。<br />\n<br />\n每星期揀一個日子為香港跳閘日。<br />\n好處，如果有2至3成日成工跳閘，係咪已經可以影響到佢地盈利，而當大家都習慣咗之後，可以由跳一日，增加到兩日或更多。<br />\n呢個方法相信後生嘅可以大力支持，不景一家大細無辦法參與。<br />\n<br />\n你唔俾我塞機場，咁塞地鐵站囉。<br />\n每個星期擇個好日，大家乖乖地塞爆香港，金鐘，中環尖咀等地鐵。大家可以睇下係未入閘前嘅地方睇下書，聽下歌，表現下又或者等下人。務求塞到你做唔到生意。<br />\n好處，一蚊都唔俾你賺，每次係適當時間塞你2到3個鐘，而人數幾千人已經夠。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多d開post討論下有乜方法，唔可以再俾政府咁玩🐶我地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9f81f56a750c934c7e9e5184b9a2ccfb20d798","tid":1500680,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:17:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d6f8ba8896ea11c95d8a8340d7696c41d27b5368","tid":1500680,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87aed651c26cfbd579942d3e107e7edd49a719fb","tid":1500680,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cf329bf05cf41013b20bfcdc8697a85fc6c310","tid":1500680,"uid":279043,"like":0,"dislike"